                    Employee Management System
                </h2>

                <p class="text-center text-muted fs-5 mb-4">
                    A centralized web-based platform for managing employee information
                    and administrative operations within an organization.
                </p>

                <hr />

                <!-- SYSTEM OVERVIEW -->
                <p class="fs-6 text-muted">
                    The <strong>Employee Management System (EMS)</strong> is designed to help
                    organizations efficiently manage employee data through a secure,
                    admin-controlled platform. The system enables administrators and HR
                    personnel to maintain accurate employee records and streamline
                    organizational processes.
                </p>

                <p class="fs-6 text-muted">
                    By centralizing employee information, the system improves data
                    accessibility, reduces manual effort, and ensures consistency
                    across departments.
                </p>

                <hr class="my-4" />

                <!-- MANAGEMENT & FEATURES -->
                <div class="row">

                    <!-- WHO MANAGES -->
                    <div class="col-md-6 mb-4">
                        <h5 class="fw-semibold mb-3">
                            <i class="bi bi-person-gear text-primary me-2"></i>
                            System Management
                        </h5>
                        <ul class="list-unstyled text-muted">
                            <li>• Managed by Administrators and HR personnel</li>
                            <li>• Secure access to employee information</li>
                            <li>• Centralized control over organizational data</li>
                            <li>• Structured department-wise management</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>

                    <!-- KEY FEATURES -->
                    <div class="col-md-6 mb-4">
                        <h5 class="fw-semibold mb-3">
                            <i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill text-success me-2"></i>
                            Key Features
                        </h5>
                        <ul class="list-unstyled text-muted">
                            <li>• Create, update, view, and delete employee records</li>
                            <li>• Search and filter employees by multiple criteria</li>
                            <li>• Dashboard overview for quick insights</li>
                            <li>• Export employee data for reporting purposes</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>

                </div>

                <hr class="my-4" />

                <!-- TECHNOLOGY STACK -->
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-md-12 text-center">
