                        </h5>
                        <p class="text-muted mb-1">ASP.NET Core MVC</p>
                        <p class="text-muted mb-1">Entity Framework Core</p>
                        <p class="text-muted mb-1">SQL Server</p>
                        <p class="text-muted mb-1">Bootstrap 5</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <hr class="my-4" />

                <p class="text-center text-muted mb-0">
                    This system provides a structured and reliable approach to handling
                    employee records within an organization.
                </p>

            </div>
        </div>

    </div>
</div>

